# MyTest.calls downstream

## Inbound Requests

#### POST /api/data → myapp.com

**Request** `POST /api/data HTTP/1.1`

| Header | Value |
|---|---|
| Content-Type | application/json |
| Host | myapp.com |

<details><summary>Body</summary>

```json
{
    "name": "test",
    "value": 42
}
```

</details>

**Response** `HTTP/1.1 200 OK`

| Header | Value |
|---|---|
| Content-Type | application/json |

<details><summary>Body</summary>

```json
{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "test",
    "value": 42
}
```

</details>

## Outbound Requests

#### DELETE /foobar → downstream.example.com

**Request** `DELETE https://downstream.example.com/foobar HTTP/1.1`

| Header | Value |
|---|---|
| Host | downstream.example.com |

**Response** `HTTP/1.1 500 Internal Server Error`

| Header | Value |
|---|---|
| Content-Type | text/plain |

<details><summary>Body</summary>

```
something went wrong
```

</details>
